column5: Thanks again all.  Got home from work and this beautiful bouquet was waiting for me    I also got this (the only thing fishing related, so I'll post it)    Going out for dinner shortly.  Cheers all and thanks for the happy birthdays today  Joey
Did Paul claim that he bought them??? Next time I'd better deliver them in person...
Happy birthday to Joey and Art
Happy birthday Joey!
Happy Birthday!
